{"tid":1607924,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【兩張圖，請找到不同之處】","createTime":"2019-10-01T05:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T05:51:32.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dccedc4101ab124a4a13abd59c528cd7f6cfedc8","tid":1607924,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rovj7Ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRovj7Ea.jpg&h=c13f2107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/tmp_images/article_images/83496/97d880aa4dc73b05759cb675becef0b49f69de18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Ftmp_images%2Farticle_images%2F83496%2F97d880aa4dc73b05759cb675becef0b49f69de18.jpg&h=66e8d1d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f9e8e22f8c8b2e6bd2dd9b0be68bcdb0543b056","tid":1607924,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:50:03.000Z","msg":"1.condom to be<br />\n2.condom"},{"pid":"f869805ce8f14b7a84ad120d66f93cf0bba9549d","tid":1607924,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:50:51.000Z","msg":"<strong>我以颱風風眼橫過比喻，預測閱兵期間香港唔會發生衝突</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">昨日警察不斷恐嚇大家十一唔好出，同埋有很多假消息話各地暴徒會燒商場，呢個奇怪現象同早幾日批不反對通知書後立即大搜捕完全不同，<span style=\"color: red;\">就係因為警察知道，十一當日唔可以捉人、唔可以出現血腥畫面，</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">但中共又唔容許有大量人上街反共反雜，所以先嚇定大家。<br />\n</span><br />\n現在就好似颱風風眼即將略過時候，警察瘋狂捉人，製造白色恐怖。<span style=\"color: red;\">風眼將會在閱兵期間橫過香港，忽然晴天萬里，到時候社會上一定太平無事，警察唔會拉人，大家可以放膽出街。</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">但要小心，當10月1日半夜過後，就有可能好似風眼過後，又出現狂風暴雨，</span>所以大家意見表達完結後，就盡快返歸，唔好戀戰。<br />\n<br />\n點解警察聽日閱兵期間唔捉人？<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為北大人唔想在世界各地直播閱兵期間，同時直播出現血腥鎮壓嘅場面，咁會落佢面，令雜種即時受到黨內外以及西方社會譴責，</span>所以十一閱兵嘅時候唔會清場鎮壓。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽講呢個安排僅十一閱兵嘅時段限定！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1606271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1606271</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日香港慘劇係雜種一手造成，冤有頭債有主，請大家對準政權目標<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有明確訊息證實係習近平一人當日堅持拒絕「撤回」及下令將44人極速起訴暴動！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602129\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一遊行要高叫「天滅中共！習近平全家死」口號落中共面！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0868b2c24dcfc611ad3ec92cc61e26b9d4c86d3c","tid":1607924,"uid":280752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:51:32.000Z","msg":"一個未坐監"}]}